verbose_text: Although HU/Ap treatment did not disrupt EC motile selection, unlike loss of tm4sf18 (XREF_FIG A versus XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G), and mutation of tm4sf18 did not disrupt EC proliferation, unlike HU/Ap (XREF_FIG B versus S3H), both tm4sf18 mutation and HU/Ap treatment generated very similar and prolonged reductions in ISV cellularity (XREF_FIG D and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY I).
